Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.89,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Let's recap the show so far!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.36,0:00:08.15,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori Gotoh is a slightly shy, socially \Nanxious, and isolated guitar enthusiast!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This guitar's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.60,0:00:16.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But some day, I might like to join a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.16,DefaultTop,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,And as she was thinking that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come join our band!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:23.79,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,From that humble beginning, she formed a rock\Nband with this group of colorful characters!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.33,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, her life has been \None event after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.33,0:00:27.96,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,And just now, the club manager said,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:31.05,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,"I can't put you on stage \Nunless you pass an audition,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.88,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,which inspired a huge panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.09,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(816,1)\fnTimes New Roman\c&H403537&\3c&HAEA6A5&\bord2\pos(318.5,201.5)}Manager's             Authority
