Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:52.40,Default,Kessoku Band,0000,0000,0000,,Hooray! Hooray! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:50.76,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,They managed to pass their audition!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.40,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness bloomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:56.84,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,Or so they thought, but Hitori Gotoh \Nstill had a towering wall before her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.84,0:00:57.86,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:01.36,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,That five-person ticket quota!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:05.04,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,What was a girl with no contacts \Noutside of her family and band to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.01,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:07.64,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Hitori—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Only ten days to the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.17,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.3\pos(320.5,292.5)\c&HFFFFF7&\fscy110\fsp1}Last Night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:22.76,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Father, mother, sister, dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:25.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,One ticket left for...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.63,0:01:27.66,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.66,0:01:31.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I doubt she'd make the three-hour trip \Njust to see me play...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:31.08,DefaultTop,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Good.{bg}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:33.80,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,You know Jimihen can't come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.00,0:01:42.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I s-sort of had a feeling, \Nbut... I wasn't sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:45.91,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Futari can't go to a club like that either.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.28,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,She's only five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.28,0:01:50.01,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:51.84,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary in there.
