Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.83,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right to the liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:43.35,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver! Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:46.70,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd really \Nbuy me the miso soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:47.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:52.01,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna take off my head and power-wash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:54.26,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up helping a very weird person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:55.13,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna take out my guts \Nand wring out all the alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.17,0:06:58.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I should be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.50,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.82,0:07:04.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hitori Gotoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.88,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What a cute name!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:08.81,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.49,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Drinking should be done \Nin moderation, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.49,0:07:15.04,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,She said as she started drinking again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:17.37,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hair of the dog that bit ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.25,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.25,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(106,1)\an8\fnGeorgia\c&H0B0E0F&\3c&HD0DED0&\bord2\4c&H4847CF&\shad1.5}Onikoro Sake
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:32.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's still drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? Just leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.22,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Ya want some too, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.56,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's the cheap stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.62,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:42.74,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're underage, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.77,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you listenin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.58,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's way too weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:48.01,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't ya said anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:51.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if she's \Nserious or playing dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.07,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan, you're cold as ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.49,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Like concrete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,On the count of three, I book it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:57.00,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whaddya want? \NYa want some booze after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:58.41,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I sh-should be going...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.25,0:08:03.92,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.41,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Do ya play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:08.75,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a band too! Indie, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She plays too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:12.68,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can ya play?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-s-s-so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've never talked to a \Ngrown-up rocker before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:20.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I d-don't know why, but I bet she'll be mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.60,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(154,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\c&HBECC49&\3c&H899256&\bord1\pos(491,50)}Lemme see\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hLemme see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.08,0:08:21.71,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see! Lemme see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.86,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.61,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know what rock is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:31.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get out of here \Nbefore I say something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:33.27,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.27,0:08:36.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A-Actually I bought it \Nbut gave up after one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.53,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I was just heading \Nto a pawn shop to sell it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:39.16,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping for a far more worthy \Nperson to use this guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.75,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and truly find their wings and soar, \Nbut I d-d-don't play at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:47.27,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Gosh, wonder how much I'll get for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:49.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's all-you-can-eat yakiniku for me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.96,0:08:49.79,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:55.01,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Giving up after one day is a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.17,0:08:59.64,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You can sell it any time you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.20,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But if you stick with it \Na little while longer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.30,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,you might become worthy \Nof that guitar someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:09.52,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, listen to me! Tryin' to sound all wise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:09.52,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Is she kind of normal after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.35,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.35,0:09:14.64,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,How's about I give you lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, actually, sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.36,0:09:20.74,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I lied about everything I said just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:22.54,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's a heck of a smooth lie you told.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.43,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, nice guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:30.16,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear you take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.16,0:09:32.21,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.45,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I play bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:38.18,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Booze and the bass are \Nworth more to me than my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:40.60,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,so I always keep them close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.29,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your bass?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.65,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\c&H61ABDA&\frz350.3\move(560.07,66.46,569.68,68.87,23,607)}Tee hee hee
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.58,0:09:52.65,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I left it at the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:54.86,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go grab it, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She values her life so little...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard back from Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.68,0:10:06.20,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Still left on read.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.06,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we shouldn't have \Nsent those LOINEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Today's our practice day.
