Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.08,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is all too incomprehensible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.03,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Super Ultra Shuten Doji EX!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.03,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm struggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:40.54,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.56,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. Very cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.45,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We really rocked the house \Nat our concert last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.21,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But I drank way too much at the afterparty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.52,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Next thing I knew, the sun was up,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:53.36,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,and I had no idea where I was!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.80,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-How many hours did you spend drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.36,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Lesse...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.02,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The afterparty started at ten, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.64,0:11:04.20,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I was pretty out of it \Nmost of the time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:07.72,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Figure I might as well stay up 'til tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:10.87,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You really like drinking that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:15.13,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sure do! Drinking lets me forget \Neverything, so I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.13,0:11:16.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.94,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like fears about the future.
