Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's really sympathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.76,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Selling tickets is so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.76,0:13:02.77,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I really struggled with it at the start too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.71,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, it really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.71,0:13:06.90,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, since you saved my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.35,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna put some skin in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.68,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Now, prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:16.56,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:21.98,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,play a street concert, right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Street concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.95,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You've got those flyers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.95,0:13:35.50,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The best way to sell tickets is to play \Non the street and pick up an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.83,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.28,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Seems there's some kind of \Nfestival in the area today,
