Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.29,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,so there's lots of people around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.29,0:13:43.68,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect for a street performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.68,0:13:47.67,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we don't have amps and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:50.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,T-Too bad! Guess we'll have \Nto try another time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.78,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:54.47,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.89,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna play on the street, \Nso could you bring the stuff by for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.47,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, the equipment's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:02.15,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do I do? She's really going for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.12,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:02.15,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, thanks!
