Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.03,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.42,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.42,0:14:13.20,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,It's free, so come by if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.04,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanazawa-Hakkei peeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:18.35,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.09,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Come watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.02,0:14:25.24,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're playing, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:29.63,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You've never played outside before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.59,0:14:34.76,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that scared, \Nyou could shut your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:37.46,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Or... Well, I guess you're \Nscared of strangers, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:38.31,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that might just work...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.31,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I feel you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:42.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've been playing so long in the dark\Nwhere I can't see my fingers anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.38,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,But just so you know...
