Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:51.57,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in combat with \Nthe people in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.09,0:14:56.83,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get it twisted who your enemies are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:00.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What does she mean, enemies?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:08.05,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's Gotoh-san like at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:08.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can kind of picture it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.64,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Is she a loner at school, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:24.41,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,We're in different classes, so I don't see \Nwhat she's like with her classmates, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:28.06,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I've never seen her\Nwith another person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:31.81,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's not being bullied \Nor anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:37.95,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She's really withdrawn and people seem \Nto have trouble interacting with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:41.68,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of hard to know\Nhow to approach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:42.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.75,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But Bocchi's so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:51.86,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:56.12,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,We're playing an original song \Nby her band, Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.60,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.18,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, play.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She'll stick with me for guitar practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:15.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,but when I invite her to have lunch \Nwith my friends, she won't come,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.15,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and she's never in her classroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's ad-libbing, but she's really selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:26.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Her playing is so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's giving me such a firm \Nfoundation to play from.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:34.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Just from hearing her play, \NI can tell she's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.38,0:16:37.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,By comparison, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they're all \Nlaughing at me out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:41.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too scared to look up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.36,0:16:44.39,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:48.26,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.26,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Well... The guitar girl seemed nervous, \Nso it just came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:52.69,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,Just came out?
