Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.32,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,1)\b0\c&H546D77&\fs20\pos(155,313.5)}Read by 3
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.32,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(280,1)\an4\b0\c&H30684A&\fs20\pos(231,192)\3c&H7AFF9A&\bord2}How are you doing, Bocchi-chan?\NComing to practice today? \NI want to try the new song all together!
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.34,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I sure hope she's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:02.95,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:05.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I never had any enemies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.92,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,She opened her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.51,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Her playing is suddenly more stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:21.47,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,So this is how Hitori-chan plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:23.77,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.78,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:31.89,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The only people here are the ones \Nwho stopped to hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.31,0:17:42.29,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing and conquering her flaws \Nin such a short time... Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.25,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.93,0:17:48.05,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,My instinct never lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:54.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They're all smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.32,0:17:58.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I do more concerts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,will I see more faces like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,518)\an7\bord0\blur0.4\alpha&H55&\p1\c&HACA0A2&\fscx174\fscy122\pos(18,108.5)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,518)\an8\fnArial Black\fs18\c&H271F13&\3c&H968A9A&\pos(104,113.5)}Special Performance\NBuy tickets, please!\N— Kessoku Band —\N1500 yen per ticket\NPerforming 8/14, 6PM\N at Kitazawa STARRY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:12.39,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:16.94,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Great work, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.94,0:18:19.13,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:24.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't realize I only had one eye open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:25.99,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:31.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(145,518)\an7\bord0\blur0.4\alpha&H55&\p1\c&HB6B8C1&\fscx174\fscy122\pos(433.5,29.5)}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.25,0:18:31.04,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(145,518)\an8\fnArial Black\fs18\c&H271F13&\3c&H968A9A&\pos(519.5,34.5)}Special Performance\NBuy tickets, please!\N— Kessoku Band —\N1500 yen per ticket\NPerforming 8/14, 6PM\N at Kitazawa STARRY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.99,0:18:27.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, n-nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:31.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't change everything all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.95,0:18:33.04,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.84,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Can we buy tickets to this concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.16,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.45,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Hitori-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.78,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you freeze up from joy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.44,0:18:51.06,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Um... That'll be 1,500 yen apiece, 3,000 total!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:52.22,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:53.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:57.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you sure you want \Nto buy those t-t-tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.48,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up already, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:01.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.74,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,This was my first time watching a \Nstreet performance, but you were so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:07.81,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the good work at \Nyour next concert, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.81,0:19:10.80,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right... I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:15.94,Default,Fan 2,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be playing that song again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:18.46,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H1D1919&\pos(203.5,101.5)\3c&HACA2A6&\bord2}Onikoro
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.59,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.59,0:19:19.18,Default,Fan 1,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait to see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:23.04,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,To think I had this shining \Nperiod myself once...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:25.76,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, I drown away my cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.25,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:29.39,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:32.10,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back in my happiness spiral soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't possibly be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:39.20,Default,Cop,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. You guys can't play here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.61,DefaultTop,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's the fuzz!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:42.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Are they gonna take me away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.52,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:48.49,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,They {\i1}are{\i0} pretty mad, though, \Nso let's call it quits here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:54.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:59.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I got so carried away before, but I \Nstill have one ticket left to sell...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:02.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I did sell four!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.64,0:20:04.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for my first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.98,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy that last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:09.09,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,The ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.09,0:20:10.70,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,That'll get you to your quota, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.35,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:17.47,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I typically operate \Nout of Shinjuku, so I'm close by,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.40,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,and I know this club too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:25.97,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,A concert costing over five Onikoros...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:27.26,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,It'd better be worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.41,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.97,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Let's play together again some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.97,0:20:33.75,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.09,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,What a mysterious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:43.01,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Rockers really are...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:45.18,DefaultItalics,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.76,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I spent the last of my money on your ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:54.07,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow some for the train?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.07,0:20:57.98,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay you back at the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:57.98,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This feels strangely familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:20:58.92,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:01.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Why are rockers all so poor?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:12.87,Default,Fan 1/Fan 2/Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:23.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't make it to practice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:24.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I sold all my tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And... send!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,May our concert be a big success!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:43.29,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,"Also, I sold all \Nmy tickets," she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.93,0:21:45.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.18,0:21:47.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She's totally lying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.10,0:21:47.95,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.67,0:21:52.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I bet our LOINEs really \Ndid put pressure on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:54.10,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.08,0:21:58.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all be nice to her \Nat practice tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:21:59.55,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.71,0:21:59.55,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:21.42,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,I sleep, with big problems \Nweighing down on me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:32.08,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,Though you can't beat that feeling \Nof being loved, it's true
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:41.76,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,When I awaken from cold dreams, \Nmy body feels numb
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.76,0:22:50.50,Songs_ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shine so brightly, \Nit could make me a shadow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.54,0:22:55.38,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to take that step
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.38,0:23:03.10,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Though there's nothing certain about it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:10.23,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It carries my childish heart into tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.60,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to blast out the thoughts \Nrattling around in my brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.18,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,And live, to its fullest, a life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.18,0:23:22.16,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been taking advances on for so long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.16,0:23:24.67,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,But I also love the days I spend \Nlying around, doing nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.67,0:23:27.29,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,So I know I'm going to go see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.29,0:23:33.09,Songs_ED2b,,0000,0000,0000,,Before it all disappears some day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.97,0:23:39.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H8A51D9&\pos(309,49.5)}#07  To Your House
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.78,Default,Kikuri,0000,0000,0000,,Wash'it!
